{"tid":1537372,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"11月區議會選舉 - 和理非回合","createTime":"2019-09-04T01:58:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T03:35:27.000Z","uid":32934,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"85364c1d5719c584a22caf102981a2a8a3b258be","tid":1537372,"uid":32934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:58:45.000Z","msg":"到時希望大家投票, 亦小心選舉條例<br />\n唔好唔小心令你支持既候選人失去參選資格, OK?<br />\n拎返區議會, 下年拎返立法會<br />\n唔好俾獻世派呢一年有翻盤既空間!"},{"pid":"080b812f67ae3942ecc7f7a93528011a936d5935","tid":1537372,"uid":267425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:58:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>解散警隊 刻不容緩</strong></span></span><br />\n我屌曬你地老母快啲推第六大訴求<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1536852\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1536852</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fLDFcUN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfLDFcUN.jpg&h=350c6ca1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ad0ae93c396e0c5e6073eddb724f6d9e95ea2dc3","tid":1537372,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:58:55.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"426fbe109dce67bf1b8682a02df5058c14edb68e","tid":1537372,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:19:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全民抗爭，長久戰、拖垮邪惡、打倒腐敗<br />\n<br />\n每日任務：<br />\n1. 抵制支持「邪惡」「無良」的商店，例如cctvb廣告、黨鐵商埸、黑社會、打壓員工的店鋪、減少淘寶<br />\n2. 安全情況下跳閘，免費搭港鐵<br />\n3. 夜晚十點咆哮！！！<br />\n4. 做運動，身體健康，鬥長命<br />\n4. 每日一個post，社交媒體戰（Twitter, IG, Facebook, Reddit)<br />\n#FreeHongKong #HongKongProtest #Chinazi<br />\n5. 不要說推，試著將呢段訊息copy and paste嚟推post<br />\n<br />\n每星期任務：<br />\n1. 罷買Bye Buy Day：星期日、星期五(唔買非必需品）<br />\n2. 每星期做孝子，關心下老母老豆老人家，自己老母自己救<br />\n3. 每星期去連儂牆貼3張文宣<br />\n<br />\n每月任務：<br />\n1. 出糧換美金、買美股、少碰中港股票<br />\n2. MPF都買美股<br />\n3. 搵多幾個人參與<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持到尾，Best effort，你呢？<br />\nVersion 2019.09.04"},{"pid":"20aab5197285b4442cef91321aa1ab3a7bcb6981","tid":1537372,"uid":241904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:22:02.000Z","msg":"其實區議會好重要<br />\n區議會其實係立法會前哨戰<br />\n點解咁講?因為區議員會為立法會議員拉票,曾經聽過D紅底人士講,一個區議員可以拉到3000街坊票, 如果10個區議員chur晒咁幫一個立法會議候選人拉票,佢就好大機會做到<br />\n其次,每個區如果民主派區議員過半數,果一區既區議會主席就會歸民主派,咁樣區議會先可以討論番果一區既街坊真正同佢地有關既議題<br />\n最後而最重要,就係區議員佔特首選委會10.25%,即係123票,除左6票係超級區議員,其他117票點黎?係由相應地區的區議員互選產生,基本上即係話,只要民主派係每個區都過半數,咁果117票就會比晒民主派!!!!<br />\n117票差唔多可以推走到當年777, 689已經收左皮啦<br />\n所以區議會到底有幾重要你知道未呀"},{"pid":"1a3774bd12c9f32b451e8973faa4af972580beb6","tid":1537372,"uid":265234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:23:16.000Z","msg":"有咩情況選民會令候選人失去參選資格?<br />\n<br />\n(反過來玩可以好好玩)"},{"pid":"e6e93773ecda743fef976f7a1e21be18c3dfba36","tid":1537372,"uid":134107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:47:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B8W7Cuk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB8W7Cuk.jpg&h=a399d20e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[10月1送大禮]「和理拍」一齊推上聯合國人權理事會！！!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1536307\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1536307</a>"},{"pid":"086211d56537bcb485a8478a9caebaf30898cad6","tid":1537372,"uid":41477,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:52:08.000Z","msg":"Plan b, 要有素人做backup, 佢癲起上黎真係dq 晒全部泛民"},{"pid":"8d6ad75ac93007685add99a16662ff0c11371313","tid":1537372,"uid":293698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:54:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"af29137008b0668c185d6d3be19a758a17977d12","tid":1537372,"uid":215861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d6ad75ac93007685add99a16662ff0c11371313","tid":1537372,"uid":293698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"086211d56537bcb485a8478a9caebaf30898cad6","tid":1537372,"uid":41477,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:52:08.000Z","msg":"Plan b, 要有素人做backup, 佢癲起上黎真係dq 晒全部泛民"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:54:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T03:35:27.000Z","msg":"毒辣自治嗰班就DQ啦"}]}